{
  "stem": "3453.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one woman-- brief-- came up to him and she said, where are you taking us?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, we are taking you to a working camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this where they took us in the outskirts of our town, where this camp was erected.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there where I first saw that camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were three big barracks, wooden barracks, a toilet for men open on one side, a toilet for woman, double barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People already were-- when we-- when they brought us in, the people from the small town they brought them in a night before, a day before, and they were already down there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we saw already dead bodies by the barbed wire, double barbed wire, by the barbed wire, and the blood was already dry.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they pushed us in, in that enclosure.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the Germans with the machine guns was sitting on the hill, facing us between this-- this double barbed wire with a German, a Ukrainian with guns.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They got all the Jews from-- from Sarny and from the surrounding-- OK, what happened--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--towns.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then, I start running around, and I see my relatives.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I see my relatives from my small town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went up to a group of people, my mother with me, and I-- their name was [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Pomerance. ?] They have relatives and their grandchildren right in Washington.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I came up to them and my great uncle, this saint of a man, was sitting down there on the ground and praying to God.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I guess God was not with him and against him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the whole family surrounded him.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
